             <h1 class="">Bootstrap Boilerplate</h1>
            <p class="intro">I have created this boilerplate as a starting point for future projects.</p>
            <p class="intro">The default bootstrap grid has been adjusted a little to reduce the gutter-width between columns, which I have always found to be a little wide. Details of this can be seen on the <a href="structure.html">Structure</a> page.</p>
            <p class="intro">I have also created stylesheets for <a href="typography.html">typography</a> and a set of default Navbars. Other elements may be added as I create them.</p>
            <p class="intro">The boilerplate has been constructed using <a href="https://codekitapp.com/" target="_blank">CodeKit</a>. <br/>Feel free to <a href="https://github.com/SimonSharville/Bootstrap_Boilerplate" target="_blank">fork</a> it and use as you wish.</p>
